title: Hour 2 - Daniel Snyder Dirt, Brent Musburger
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Daniel Snyder Dirt, Brent Musburger
description:
Dan talks to legendary broadcaster Brent Musburger about his career, the Las Vegas Raiders and the rest of the NFL. And the Danettes chime in on the latest report that Washington Commanders Owner, Daniel Snyder has been collecting dirt on other owners as well as NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
